name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Darrian DEANS, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Darrian DEANS, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of May, 2011, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel of record shall file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order. The Motion for Appointment of Counsel is DISMISSED AS MOOT.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

20 A.3d 1192
COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Darrian DEANS, Petitioner.

May 25, 2011.
